.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_open_voting -  This function setups if the votes should be open or not.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_open_voting(int open)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^open%^RESET%^ - 1 for an open system 0 for closed

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/voting_room.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function setups if the votes should be open or not.  If a vote is
open then you know who voted for each thing.
.EP

